collections.name: Mars Walker Shoe Collection
collections.description: This NFT collection features 500 assets of shoes designed by Mars Walker digital technologists. Each NFT represents a unique original concept shoe or digital product. Offering the owner not only a stunning digital artwork but also exclusive rights to ownership of the shoe's patent and trademark. By owning a NFT in the collection, holders gain access to Certificates of Ownership and Authenticity, and product protection, ensuring their place in the Mars Walker brand’s future. The NFTs are hosted on the Ethereum blockchain and are transferable with lifetime validity. The Priest shoe incorporates the concept of Physical Shoe Tokenization (PST) by combining the digital artwork of the shoe with representations of smart contracts and provenance, evoking a sense of exclusivity and high value. Provenance automatically verifies ownership and manages the transfer of rights between the physical and digital products. Including ownership verification for future sales/resale, or product authenticity.
